track.name: I don’t even speak spanish lol - feat. Rio Santana, Judah, Andrez Babii

wiki.summary: This song was previewed on X’s Instagram in January, 2018 under the name “Through The Night.” It features Florida’s artists Judah, Carlos Andrez, and Rio Santana. This upbeat song features verses sung in Spanish, seemingly not fitting in with the rest of the album. In the first track of this album, “Introduction (Instructions),” X explains that: "this album is far different, far more versatile, far more uplifting than the last. It’s something you can find comfort in, it’s very comforting but discomforting at the same time." Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: This song was previewed on X’s Instagram in January, 2018 under the name “Through The Night.” It features Florida’s artists Judah, Carlos Andrez, and Rio Santana. This upbeat song features verses sung in Spanish, seemingly not fitting in with the rest of the album. In the first track of this album, “Introduction (Instructions),” X explains that: "this album is far different, far more versatile, far more uplifting than the last. It’s something you can find comfort in, it’s very comforting but discomforting at the same time." X also took to his Instagram on January 28th 2018 and posted the following on his story: "This albums not about the words, it’s about the feeling…it’ll be very hard to understand, but very easy to listen to…it’s not what you’re expecting, even if you feel like you understand my music, be prepared to not understand this music" Read more on Last.fm.
